videos.headline: Travis Homer takes it to the house for Miami
videos.description: Miami RB Travis Homer finds a seam and runs in for a 35-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami's Perry connects with  Cager for 26-yard TD
videos.description: Miami QB N'Kosi  Perry finds TE Lawerence Cager for a 26-yard touchdown to put the Hurricanes up 14-0.

videos.headline: Miami's Redwine gets turnover chain for INT
videos.description: Miami's  Sheldrick Redwine intercepts FIU QB James Morgan and collects the turnover chain as his prize.

videos.headline: Cager hauls in 2nd TD pass for Miami
videos.description: N'Kosi Perry connects with Lawrence Cager for a 17-yard touchdown, their second scoring connection of the day.

videos.headline: Worton puts FIU on the board in the 4th
videos.description: FIU QB James Morgan finds a wide-open CJ Worton for a 35-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: FIU's Morgan squeezes in 2nd  TD pass
videos.description: FIU QB James  Morgan rips a 5-yard touchdown pass to CJ Worton to shrink Miami's lead.
